npm init -y -->creates package.json
npm install express --save -->add to dependencies in package.json file

if u don't want to restart server every time after changes install below one
npm install nodemon --save-dev (search about it)

--for handling data of the request we need parser
npm install body-parser --save

--install mongoose for easy handling of mongo DB
npm install mongoose -save

